Instead of doing the platform check, I am now checking if duthost.is_multi_asic True or not. If true, it will restart the appropriate SWSS instance, else it will execute the default code.

@sdszhang - Thanks for the comment.

Modified the code to find the asic instance and will restart the appropriate corresponding swss instance. So in future, if there are more asics (more than 2 or 3), the code will still remain the same.

Thanks,
